NAME
       reboot - reset the computer

USAGE
       reboot

DESCRIPTION
       Reboot closes all files, and prepares your  system  for	a
       reset, it will then, if it can reset your  system.  Reboot
       can be used directly at the shell,or used in shell scripts
       for administrative jobs. Reboot must be run as root.

